This paper deals with the conversion of RDF graphs to property graphs, which is a topic related to database management (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of graph algorithms for analysis, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of SPARQL for querying RDF data, which is a topic related to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the use of graph database engines for analysis, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
